Package: ssbtools
Type: Package
Title: SSB API Tools for Data Retrieval and Caching
Version: 0.3.0
URL: https://github.com/willemdig/ssbtools
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Willem", "Ofstad",
      email = "willem.ofstad@digdir.no",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A small utility for fetching data from the Statistics Norway (SSB)
    JSON-stat API and caching it locally as CSV using hash-based change detection.
    Useful for reproducible workflows and efficient handling of open government data.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    rjstat,
    digest,
    readr,
    glue
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
